Pong game

It has two paddles and hits a moving ball.

Right player is controlled by up and down keys
Left player is controlled by w and s keys

The opposite player get a point when a player miss a point
and the ball reset the centre and changes moving direction

When a player hits the ball, they get a point and the speed
of the ball will increase.
Speed will reset when any player missed the ball.

There are two scores displayed on the screen, one for each player.
